# library/certs/server.key is a locally-generated self-signed dev cert
# used by the dev server only. It is gitignored and never shipped.
# See library/certs/README.md for the scanner-vs-git-index boundary.
#
# The HIGH finding on `library/certs/server.key` (and `.crt`) is an
# AsymmetricPrivateKey secret detection. We suppress it via the trivy.yaml
# `scan.skip-files` list (path-based secret ignores are not supported by
# `.trivyignore` in trivy 0.69). The entries below document the policy for
# future trivy versions that add path-aware suppressions.
AsymmetricPrivateKey
